results.title: Showdown At Sea
results.description: DD infiltrates Crime-Wave's lair and along with Foggy and Debbie helps to unmask him in Scooby-Doo type fashion.

results.title: Trapped By the Trio of Doom
results.description: A deadly trio of villains have turned a carnival into a death trap for DD.

results.title: Quoth the Nighthawk, "Nevermore!"
results.description: Daredevil is upstaged by the new hero in town who is only in the game for the glory.

results.title: The Girl--Or the Gladiator?
results.description: Gladiator, feigning innocence, lures Matt and Foggy to prison and tries to make a break for it; DD has to face down his old foe instead of trying to stop Karen from leaving for California.

results.title: Suddenly...the Stunt-Master!
results.description: DD is in L.A. trying to track down Karen when he runs across his old foe, the Stunt-Master.

results.title: The Murderous Menace of the Man Called Brimstone!
The Killing of Brother Brimstone
results.description: A cast member of Karen's soap opera is killing people and DD investigates.

results.title: Trapped in the Tar Pits of Death
And One Cried Murder
results.description: DD investigates the death of a star on Karen's soap opera.

results.title: Get Off the Streets! The Stilt-Man's Back In Town!
Stilt-Man Stalks the Soundstage
results.description: DD and Karen are slated to appear on Stunt-Master's new TV show but Stilt-Man interferes.

results.title: The Phoenix--The Fighter--and the Man Without Fear!
Phoenix and the Fighter
results.description: DD tries to protect a young boxer who is being trained by the same man who trained his father from the shady dealings of Kragg and the Phoenix Group.

results.title: A Life On the Line
results.description: DD and Panther take on the Thunderbolt gang with a young boy's life hanging in the balance.

results.title: In Mortal Combat With Sub-Mariner
results.description: Namor hires Franklin and Murdock to sue the human race on his behalf; When this doesn't work, he gets himself arrested so he can have his day in court; Realizing humanity won't listen, the Sub-Mariner goes on a rampage which brings Daredevil into the (hopeless) fray; Namor returns to the sea out of respect for DD and to stop Krang from taking over Atlantis.

results.title: A City in Turmoil--A City in Flame !
The Tribune
results.description: A movie mogul decides that he needs to take an active (and violent) hand in dealing with those he considers un-Americans; Daredevil intervenes.

results.title: If An Eye Offend Thee
results.description: The Tribune takes over the trial of a trio of Communist pinko hippie sympathizers.

results.title: Look Out Blind Man ! Here Comes Tagak the Leopard Lord !
Lo, the Lord of the Leopards!
results.description: DD and Tagak chase down an interdimensional thief.

results.title: Revealed at Last !! The Sinister Secret of Zodiac!
Behold the Brotherhood
results.description: The Scorpio Key transports our cast of heroes and villains to another dimension where the Brotherhood of the Ankh forces them to battle to replenish the power of the key.

results.title: In the Country of the Blind
results.description: Foggy shows up at Matt's doorstep completely blind and the two discover that many in New York have been struck with the malady; DD gets a group of genuine blind folks to help him take down the Smasher and his gang who have caused the sightless problem.

results.title: In the Sinister Shadow of...El Condor!
Now Rides the Ghost of El Condor
results.description: Matt and Foggy are in South America when they get embroiled in a revolution started by El Condor.

results.title: The Deathmarch of El Condor
results.description: Daredevil helps bring El Condor's revolution to an end.

results.title: ...And So Enters the Amazing Spider-Man
results.description: It's angst a'plenty as DD and Spidey mourn over lost love both before and during a fight with the Sub-Mariner.

results.title: On the Horns of the Man-Bull !
The Horns of the Bull
results.description: DD saves a couple from becoming a mad doctor's experiment, but the doctor uses one of his cronies for the process, turning him into the Man-Bull.

results.description: Nelson and Murdock are hired by a disgruntled scientist who claims his boss stole his invention; The scientist turns out, not only to be the real thief, but also the new villain, Stilt-Man.

results.description: DD captures the Widow as she is suspected of killing the Scorpion; Foggy is blackmailed into rushing the Widow to trial with Murdock fighting for Natasha's freedom; When DD attempts to examine the Scorpion's body, he is attacked by Mr. Hyde who blows the place up; With crucial evidence destroyed, the Widow is freed and vows to leave the country.

results.description: DD has a psychadelic fight with the Dark Messiah and his minions.
